instruction: From the text below, create a unique opening phrase for a story about a young girl who lives in a world where electricity is scarce
input: The young girl was born into a world of clashing technology and scarcity. She had been raised to understand the consequences of the world around her, yet she still dreamt of a place where electricity was abundant.
output: In a world of clashing technology and scarcity, a young girl grew up dreaming of a place where electricity was abundant.
